msgstr "**Betroffene Technologien**:"

#: ../../source/examples/pdf_chatbot.rst:13
msgid ""
"@ `Xinference <https://github.com/xorbitsai/inference>`_ as a LLM model "
"hosting service"
msgstr ""
"@ `Xinference <https://github.com/xorbitsai/inference>`_ als Hosting-Dienst "
"für LLM-Modelle"

#: ../../source/examples/pdf_chatbot.rst:15
msgid ""
"@ `LlamaIndex <https://github.com/run-llama/llama_index>`_ for orchestrating"
